We are elated to announce that Earth Rhythm is now a Plastic Neutral brand. We have pledged to eliminate plastic pollution by coming together with RePurpose Global to recycle as much plastic as we use in our operations. 👣

With the help of RePurpose & Project Neela Sapna, we as a consumer-first brand dream of returning Chennai its original dream-like beauty, helping it recover, rejuvenate, and thrive. 🌊

Let's hold hands together & save our Mother Earth.🌎
